# No Slack messaging

Do **not** send, schedule, or draft Slack messages for this project.

- Never call `slack_send_message`, `slack_schedule_message`, or `slack_send_message_draft` (plugin-slack-slack MCP).
- Do not post to Slack webhooks or use any Slack API to deliver notifications.
- If the user asks to "send on Slack" or "notify on Slack", reply in chat only — do not use Slack MCP write tools.
- Slack MCP read tools (search, read channel) are allowed only when the user explicitly asks to read Slack, not to deliver results.

This applies to data refresh workflows, automations, CI, and ad-hoc agent tasks.
